name: Pair_compareToTest
description: Unit tests for the compareTo method of the Pair class.

test_cases.name: testCompareToEqual
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method for equality between two Pairs.

test_cases.name: testCompareToLeftLess
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the left element of the first Pair is less than the left element of the second Pair.

test_cases.name: testCompareToLeftGreater
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the left element of the first Pair is greater than the left element of the second Pair.

test_cases.name: testCompareToRightLess
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the right element of the first Pair is less than the right element of the second Pair.

test_cases.name: testCompareToRightGreater
test_cases.description: Tests the compareTo method when the right element of the first Pair is greater than the right element of the second Pair.
